Detailed Description

template<typename PTYPE>
class muscle::ConduitExitArray< PTYPE >

complementary class for the Java muscle.core.JNIConduitExit using primitive type arrays, e.g.

muscle.core.JNIConduitExit<double[], Object>
use muscle::ConduitExitSingle to access single primitive data instead of arrays access an exit which yields arrays (receive)
